A. Michael Baldwin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A._Michael_Baldwin 0 A. Michael Baldwin (born Michael M. Baldwin; April 4, 1963) is an American actor, producer, and screenwriter. He came to public notice as a child actor, appearing as Mike Pearson in Phantasm (1979) and its sequels.
